purdyCommonTask is an ant macro file use to help create a quick build system using:
1) java
2) groovy
3) javadocs
4) groovydocs
5) emma
6) cobertura


the source code and test code is here just to demostrate it.  the three files you need to put in your project are:
1) build.properties
2) build.xml
3) purdyCommonTasks.xml

modify build.properties for your system

run ant

